<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Email Verification Code</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background-color: #007bff; padding: 20px; text-align: center; color: white; }
        .content { padding: 20px; background-color: #f8f9fa; }
        .footer { background-color: #f1f1f1; padding: 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; }
        .otp-box { font-size: 28px; font-weight: bold; text-align: center; margin: 30px 0; padding: 15px; background-color: #e9f0ff; border-radius: 8px; letter-spacing: 3px; }
        .note { font-size: 14px; color: #666; margin-top: 30px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Email Verification Code</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <p>Hello,</p>
        <p>You're attempting to access information related to SKU: <strong><%= sku %></strong>.</p>
        <p>To verify your identity, please use the following verification code:</p>
        
        <div class="otp-box">
            <%= otp %>
        </div>
        
        <p>This code will expire in 10 minutes for security reasons.</p>
        
        <p>If you didn't request this code, please ignore this email.</p>
        
        <div class="note">
            <p><strong>Note:</strong> Please do not reply to this email. This mailbox is not monitored.</p>
        </div>
        
        <p>Thank you,<br>The Spectra Team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        <p>Â© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Spectra Metal Transactions. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p>This email was sent to <%= email %>.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 